---
title: Invoice Creation Flow
config:
  layout: elk
  look: handDrawn
  theme: dark
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant UI as 🖥️ AddInvoiceModal
    participant Hook as 🎣 useAuth/usePerms
    participant Utils as 🛠️ utils/Auditlog
    participant Supabase as 📡 Supabase
    participant DB as 💾 PostgreSQL
    
    User->>UI: 1. Click "Add Invoice"
    UI->>Hook: 2. Fetch masters (entities, clients)
    Hook->>Supabase: 3. SELECT from entities_master
    Supabase->>DB: 4. Query entities
    DB-->>Supabase: 5. Return entities
    Supabase-->>Hook: 6. Return data
    
    Hook->>Supabase: 7. SELECT from clients_master
    Supabase->>DB: 8. Query clients
    DB-->>Supabase: 9. Return clients
    Supabase-->>Hook: 10. Return data
    
    Hook-->>UI: 11. Populate form dropdowns
    UI-->>User: 12. Show AddInvoiceModal
    
    User->>UI: 13. Fill invoice details
    User->>UI: 14. Select entity, client, amounts
    User->>UI: 15. Click "Save Invoice"
    
    UI->>UI: 16. Validate form
    Note over UI: • Non-empty fields<br/>• Valid amounts<br/>• Valid dates<br/>• Permissions check
    
    alt Validation Failed
        UI-->>User: 17. Show error message
    else Validation Passed
        UI->>Supabase: 18. INSERT into invoices table
        
        Supabase->>DB: 19. INSERT invoice record
        Note over DB: id, invoice_number,<br/>entity_id, client_name,<br/>invoice_value, date
        
        DB-->>Supabase: 20. Return inserted record
        Supabase-->>UI: 21. Confirm INSERT success
        
        UI->>Utils: 22. logExport(action=INSERT)
        Utils->>Supabase: 23. INSERT into audit_logs
        Supabase->>DB: 24. INSERT audit record
        DB-->>Supabase: 25. Confirmed
        Supabase-->>Utils: 26. Success
        
        UI->>UI: 27. Close modal
        UI->>UI: 28. Invalidate Dashboard cache
        UI-->>User: 29. Show success toast
        
        Note over DB: === REAL-TIME UPDATES ===
        
        DB->>DB: 30. Broadcast INSERT event (postgres_changes)
        Supabase->>Supabase: 31. Receive event
        Supabase->>Supabase: 32. Notify subscribers (websocket)
        
        Supabase-->>UI: 33. Emit real-time event
        UI->>UI: 34. Update component state
        UI-->>User: 35. Dashboard refreshes automatically
    end
    
    style User fill:#1e40af,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style UI fill:#059669,stroke:#10b981,color:#fff
    style Hook fill:#7c3aed,stroke:#a78bfa,color:#fff
    style Utils fill:#dc2626,stroke:#f87171,color:#fff
    style Supabase fill:#ea580c,stroke:#fb923c,color:#fff
    style DB fill:#d97706,stroke:#fbbf24,color:#fff
